data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to your dream home nestled on over 2 acres of high and dry land! Bring your horses as this land is zoned for horses as well! The roof was replaced in 2022 and the exterior paint is new! This 2 acre waterfront lot gives access to boating and fishing. This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is a true gem, offering the perfect blend of comfort and natural beauty. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warm and inviting atmosphere of the large dining room, wood flooring, and easy access to your kitchen. The kitchen offers wood cabinets with plenty of pantry space for storing all of your culinary tools. There is also an eating space at the breakfast bar, perfect for those quick morning meals. The built-in microwave and oven offer additional convenience. The indoor laundry room is located just off of the kitchen. The large family room with carpeted floors, large windows and a cozy wood burning fireplace is ideal for gatherings with friends and family, providing the perfect backdrop for creating cherished memories. The master suite is a true retreat within this home, featuring a generously sized master bathroom with large double sink vanity, soaking tub, stand up shower and walk-in closets. Whether you're unwinding after a long day or preparing for a new one, this private oasis offers the comfort and convenience you deserve. The remaining two bedrooms are amply sized and share the hall bathroom. Step outside and discover the vast beauty of your waterfront 2+ acres of land. The large back deck is perfect for al fresco dining, entertaining, or simply enjoying the serene natural surroundings. In addition, the front porch provides a welcoming spot to sip your morning coffee or watch the sunset. This property offers the rare opportunity to enjoy spacious country living while still being conveniently located to local amenities and major thoroughfares. Don't miss your chance to make this dream home a reality. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and tranquility this property has to offer!
